data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated villa, nestled in Majestic Isles.  This 3 BR, 2 BTH home offers a blend of comfort, style, and convenience, ideal for those seeking a serene and maintenance-free lifestyle. Enjoy modern living with a recently renovated interior, featuring new paint, a new kitchen with sleek countertops, and new bathrooms with modern fixtures and finishes.Residents have access to a variety of amenities, including a clubhouse, swimming pool, fitness center, tennis and pickle ball courts. Located close to shopping centers, medical facilities, and recreational activities. This villa is not just a home;  it offers a perfect blend of independence and community.Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your new haven.
